	<p>I just love photographing children outdoors. The children are completely relaxed and there are so many interesting, fun ways I can capture a childâ€™s personality. The natural environment allows me to use all the wonderful textures and colours of the varying seasons giving the perfect combination.</p>


	<p>One benefit of using the outdoors is there is no need to put a room aside or a hall to set up a studio but should you prefer a studio setting I am very happy to arrange this and the children will still have lots of fun!</p>


	<p>Weather&#8230; I find I can adapt to work around it, I usually find a tree or doorway we can shelter under.</p>


	<p><strong>Benefits for your nursery, school or group</strong></p>


	<p>No location fee!
Commission on all orders!
Numerous images to choose from!
I also undertake photographic work for school prospectus, promotional and marketing material.</p>


